      <description>焦半径公式 ¶ $|AF|=|AA^{\prime}|=\dfrac{p}{2}+x_A$ $|AF|=\dfrac{p}{1-\cos\theta}$ $|BF|=|BB^{\prime}|=\dfrac{p}{2}+x_B$ $|BF|=\dfrac{p}{1+\cos\theta}$ $\dfrac{1}{|AF|}+\dfrac{1}{|BF|}=\dfrac{2}{p}$ 焦点弦公式 ¶ $|AB|=x_A+x_B+p$ $|AB|=\dfrac{p}{1-\cos\theta}+\dfrac{p}{1+\cos\theta}=\dfrac{2p}{\sin^2\theta}$ $|AB|=\dfrac{2p}{\sin^2\theta}=\dfrac{2p(\sin^2\theta+\cos^2\theta)}{\sin^2\theta}=2p(1+\dfrac{1}{\tan^2\theta})=2p(1+\dfrac{1}{k^2})$</description>
